===Diphthongs and glides===
Because they may follow consonants in initial position in a word, which no other consonant can do, and also because of Hangul orthography, which transcribes them as vowels, [[semivowels]] such as {{IPA|/j/}} and {{IPA|/w/}} are sometimes considered to be elements of [[rising diphthong]]s rather than separate consonant phonemes.

